claim.claim-text:
18. A method of providing information relating to achievements within a game application program, the method comprising the steps of:
(a) displaying a graphical user interface on a display, a first portion of the graphical user interface displaying achievements in a game application program;
(b) receiving an indication, via the user interface selection device, of a particular achievement displayed on the graphical user interface in said step (a);
(c) displaying, on a second portion of the graphical user interface, a description of the particular achievement indicated in said step (b); and
(d) downloading the game application program into the gaming and media system over a network connection.
